<template>
    <ProfileRow :imsgp='iMsgP' :menulist='menuList' :imsg='iMsg' :imsgb='iMsg2' :imsgt='imsgt' :heightList='heightList'></ProfileRow>
</template>

<script>
// @ is an alias to /src
import ProfileRow from '@/components/row/ProfileRow'
import * as request from '../../network/request'



export default {
  name: 'Page',
  components: {
    ProfileRow,
  },
  data(){
    return{
      iMsgP:'',
      menuList:[],
      iMsg:'',
      iMsg2:'',
      imsgt:'',
      heightList:[]
    }
  },
  created() {
    request.request({
      url:'http://39.107.227.252/getParagraphDetail/',
      data:{'pid': 1, 'code': 0},
      method: 'post',
    }).then(res =>{
      this.iMsgP = res.data.paragraph
      this.menuList = res.data.Info.menuList
      this.iMsg = res.data.Info.iMsg
      this.iMsg2 = res.data.Info.iMsg2
      this.imsgt = res.data.Info.imsgt
      this.heightList = res.data.Info.heightList
    }).catch(err =>{
      console.log(err);
    })
  }
}

</script>
